es loan against property, equipment finance, working capital finance, and supply chain finance for micro, small and medium enterprises (MSME); asset management and trusteeship services; insurance broking and advisory services; and engages in the life, health, motor, and property insurance distribution. It serves retail and commercial customers, individuals, and entrepreneurs, as well as businesses operating in agriculture, transportation, and small and medium enterprises. Mahindra & Mahindra Financial Services Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India. Mahindra & Mahindra Financial Services Limited is a subsidiary of Mahindra & Mahindra Limited."}}